  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to explore the experiences and perceptions of District VI
      pediatric clinicians on parental vaccine hesitancy and vaccine refusal.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a retrospective, convenience sample, descriptive study. Participants will be asked to
      complete a web-based survey on parental vaccine hesitancy/ vaccine refusal. Survey responses
      are primarily categorical. Frequencies and averages will be reported using group statistics.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
